text: Læa cng prahatprahar phwk khea n thi dı ktam thi phwk cea phb phwk khea læa cng khab li phwk khea xxk cak thi thi phwk khea khey khab li phwk cea xxk læa kar kx khwam wunway nan rayræng ying kwa kar prahatprahar seiy xik læa cng xya su rb kab phwk khea n xal-masyidi l ha rxm cnkwa phwk khea ca tharay phwk cea nı thi nan hak phwk khea tharay phwk cea læw k cng prahatprahar phwk khea seiy chen nan hæla khux kar txbthæn kæ phu ptiseth sraththa
